overview: Dance and sing along with your favorite songs from Gabby's Dollhouse in Gabby's Dollhouse: Cat-tastic Dance Along. Inspired by the TikTok sensation of dance challenges, kids will join in on the fun and dance away with all-new music videos, remixes and more! When they're ready to wind down or need a break, go into "mindfulness mode" and enjoy a relaxing guided meditation!
title: Gabby's Dollhouse: Cat-tastic Dance Along
